Class PartTime

java.lang.Object
Employee
PartTime
public class PartTime
extends Employee
A sub-class of the Employee that shares the same information, such as profile and payment with the addition of hourly and hoursWorked that is unique to PartTime. We take in a Profile and hourly that will be saved to the respective instance variables. hoursWorked will always be set to 0 on the creation of a new instance.
Author:
Ashish Shenoy, Abimanyu Ananthu

    • calculatePayment

      public void calculatePayment()
      Overridden method from the Employee class that calculates the payment of a PartTime employee. Accomplishes this by setting the payment field through a setter method in the super class. Accomplishes this by taking the hourly and multiplying it the number of hours worked. Additional payments for each hour above 80 counts as overtime.
